The opportunity will allow this IT leader to define, develop and lead a true platform that will deliver further integration across existing portfolio companies and serve as a platform as new companies are acquired and integrated.  Including the development of the IT roadmap and execution of enterprise systems (ERP and CRM) for the company;

Responisbilities;
Provide guidance & coaching for team members to high performance standards and continued career growth.
Plan and perform database upgrades, perform database reorganizations, design and implement security strategy, and administer database performance.
